Introduction to Zhengzhou Manhole Concrete Module Production and Processing Equipment:
Zhengzhou Yixin is a professional manufacturer in China of equipment for concrete inspection well modular brick production, inspection well block machinery, and well wall module machinery, offering production lines ranging from semi-automatic to fully automated.
Through years of practice and development, we now possess high-quality equipment, mainly including hydraulic, mobile, and fully automated inspection well series equipment and supporting devices.
Inspection Well Concrete Module Production and Processing Equipment, Zhengzhou Well Wall Brick Module Equipment Assembly Site:
Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment. Characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou well wall brick module equipment:
The Yixin inspection well block brick machine equipment is widely applicable to new types of masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heating, water, electricity, and gas facilities.
Examples include various inspection wells for drainage and water storage facilities, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks, small structures, and bridge wing walls, etc.
The advantage of using concrete modules to construct inspection wells lies in the fact that the modules have ridged and grooved structures on all their sides (upper, lower, left, and right), which, when combined and stacked, form an interlocking chain.
The shear resistance of the well wall is far superior to that of masonry constructed using plain friction bonding methods.
The module has a hollow structure; after assembly and stacking, the longitudinal holes are interconnected, and the transverse holes also intersect with each other. After pouring into the cores of these holes, a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed, which serves to provide secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
The module is equipped with reinforcement slots both horizontally and vertically; the transverse and longitudinal reinforcement bars accordingly enhance the overall strength of the structure.
In addition, inspection wells and drainage wells constructed using concrete inspection well modules are less likely to experience collapse, subsidence, or leakage. The mechanical properties of the well wall modules are stable, the installation process is simple, and the formed dimensions are standardized.
The intelligent control system for concrete inspection well module brick machinery is equipped with data input and output devices, as well as a one-touch touch-screen LCD display that monitors the entire mechanical operation process. This enables ideal human-machine interaction, automatic material ratio analysis, density control, safety logic management, and a fault diagnosis system.
The mechanical-hydraulic system for the wellbore wall module adopts single-cylinder hydraulic and double-cylinder hydraulic technologies for transportation.
An independent hydraulic integration station is used to avoid the impact of main machine vibrations on the hydraulic system, thereby ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system's operation.
The equipment for manufacturing concrete inspection well modular bricks features a material distribution box, a traveling mold box, and a mold release mechanism with ascending functionality. The door of the material storage box closes automatically, and the automatic conveying pallets are also operated independently by a hydraulic system. This design ensures that all processes are completed independently by
The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment adopts imported computers, electrical components, seals, and hydraulic parts, ensuring the overall stability and reliability of the equipment.
The mechanical vibration platform for the wellbore wall module is constructed using integral sheet steel. The tabletop is precision-cut using wire cutting technology, with no welding points at all. This design allows the filler box to swing freely and be accurately guided, thereby significantly reducing mechanical wear and tear.
Reduce the mold load, combine the packing process with dual-amplitude vibration encryption in one step, and adopt an integrated, fully synchronized system that includes both table vibration and mold vibration to ensure optimal compaction results.
The well wall module is mechanically excited using specialized equipment, with the vibration amplitude automatically controlled by a computer based on the cost-effectiveness of the raw materials. This system eliminates wear and tear during braking, thereby extending the service life of the module and reducing costs.
The well wall module is equipped with both mechanical automatic control and manual control functions.
Inspection well mold:
Yixin Brick Machine Inspection Well: Constructed using cement blocks on the surface.
A corner of Yixin Company's workshop:
Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment
The Zhengzhou well wall brick module equipment can not only produce inspection well blocks, but also various standard bricks, hollow bricks, and decorative bricks for roads.
