In her speech, Ouyang Yu first extended warm congratulations and high respect to the seven individuals who were awarded honorary doctorates. They have achieved remarkable accomplishments in various fields and made outstanding contributions to the development of their country and the progress of the world. At the same time, Ouyang Yu expressed her most sincere
