Have you encountered any issues with the required continuing education hours for the initial registration of a Level 1 Cost Engineer?
Individuals who register after the deadline must provide proof of continuing education. For late registration, a minimum of 30 hours of continuing education within the past year is required. For re-registration, a minimum of 120 hours of continuing education within the past 4 years is necessary. Additionally, for each full
Continuing Education Fee Standards for Cost Engineers
Cost engineers participating in online continuing education must pay learning fees to the respective management institutions upon registration. Generally, the standard is 300 yuan per person per year for 30 hours of compulsory courses (including the unified continuing education textbooks).
The cost for a 30-hour elective course is 300 yuan per person per year.
The cost for 30 hours of compulsory courses and 30 hours of elective courses is 600 yuan per person per year (including the unified textbooks for continuing education).
(1) For those who participate in the online continuing education programs for registered cost engineers organized by the China Construction Cost Association or provincial and departmental management agencies, the number of study hours is calculated based on the time recorded in the online learning materials.
(II) Participation in centralized face-to-face training for registered cost engineers organized by the China Price Association or provincial and departmental management agencies, as well as various types of training courses and seminars, can be recognized as 4 academic hours per half-day.
(III) Participation in continuing education courses for cost engineers and cost estimators organized by the China Construction Cost Association, as well as provincial and departmental authorities; 10 academic hours can be recognized for each half-day of attendance.
(IV) Participation in research projects conducted by the China Pricing Association or at the provincial level, the development of industry standards, and the compilation of teaching materials is recognized as 30 academic hours per year for each project.
(VI) Participation in the compilation of textbooks for the National Cost Engineer Professional Qualification Examination, as well as in the processes of setting exam questions, reviewing answers, and grading papers, is eligible to earn 30 academic hours per year.
(VII) Papers and works related to engineering cost that are personally authored and publicly published (as evidenced by an official publication number).
For each 10,000 words of published works, 12 academic hours are recognized.
For papers published in national-level journals, 8 academic hours are recognized per thousand words; for papers published in provincial-level journals, 5 academic hours are recognized per thousand words; and for papers published in municipal-level journals, 3 academic hours are recognized per thousand words.
(9) Participation in public training programs organized by engineering cost consulting enterprises that have been approved or authorized by the China National Price Association, provincial-level management agencies, and provincial cost associations (excluding general corporate management and skills training) is eligible for recognition of 4 academic hours per half-day, with a maximum of 3
Online Continuing Education Learning Process for Cost Engineers
Once the registration fee is received by the registration authority, the student’s account is immediately activated, and the cost engineer can then log in to the online education classroom using their username and password to begin their studies.
Students learn through methods such as accessing on-demand courseware, asking questions for answers, and participating in online discussions.
If you forget your password and encounter an error stating that either the username or password is incorrect when trying to log in, preventing you from accessing the learning materials, please contact the registration institution you are affiliated with. The registration institution can assist you in changing your password (but they cannot change your username). Then, use the
